&lt;p&gt;The Gravesend Health Visiting team are looking for enthusiastic health visitors to join our dynamic team. If you are newly qualified or if you are an experienced HV you are very welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The CQC has rated us ‘outstanding’ and says that our colleagues feel supported, valued and respected, with high levels of staff and patient satisfaction. We proudly maintain the outstanding status with the work we complete every day.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our vision is to deliver excellent local services which improve the health of our communities. To do this we need outstanding people who share our values (CARE). CARE stands for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compassionate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aspirational&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsive&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held on 17th December 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rebecca - District Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone: 07919411179&lt;/p&gt;
